Johannesburg- Trevor Noah’s girlfriend Minka Kelly has recently taken to social media to endorse South Africa after she had a fun holiday experience in Cape Town. Trevor and Minka started dating in 2020 but split early in 2021 but later got back together again. The couple spent their summer holiday down in the beautiful mother city with some of Trevor’s friends. “Take a trip to South Africa. Find friends like these. Have the holiday of a lifetime. Thank you, Mzansi,” she wrote.  Check out some of their holiday snaps with Anele Mdoda, Khaya Dlanga and Sizwe Dhlomo.    Also Read: Look: Trevor Noah spends summer holiday with his friends For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here